rce_DxSubUnits.cmd:
WITH SRC_fact_offering_instance  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_fact_offering_instance.partner_key AS PARTNER_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.person_key AS PERSON_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.offering_key AS OFFERING_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.mailed_date AS MAILED_DATE
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.order_date AS ORDER_DATE
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.person_key  AS V_PERSON_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.intervention_key  AS V_INTERVENTION_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.offering_key  AS V_OFFERING_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.partner_key  AS V_PARTNER_KEY
 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_FACT_OFFERING_INSTANCE SRC_fact_offering_instance  
 WHERE 
	SRC_fact_offering_instance.is_deleted = 0 
) 
,  Generate_Row_Num 
 AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_fact_offering_instance.V_PERSON_KEY AS V_PERSON_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.V_INTERVENTION_KEY AS V_INTERVENTION_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.V_OFFERING_KEY AS V_OFFERING_KEY
	,SRC_fact_offering_instance.V_PARTNER_KEY AS V_PARTNER_KEY
	,ROW_NUMBER() OVER
(
PARTITION BY
	SRC_fact_offering_instance.PERSON_KEY , SRC_fact_offering_instance.OFFERING_KEY,SRC_fact_offering_instance.PARTNER_KEY
ORDER BY
       SRC_fact_offering_instance.PERSON_KEY , SRC_fact_offering_instance.OFFERING_KEY,SRC_fact_offering_instance.PARTNER_KEY, SRC_fact_offering_instance.ORDER_DATE  desc, SRC_fact_offering_instance.MAILED_DATE  desc
) AS ROW_NUM
	,CURRENT_TIMESTAMP AS UPDATED_AT
 FROM 
	SRC_fact_offering_instance
)
UPDATE TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID 
 SET
	TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.last_order_ind = Generate_Row_Num.ROW_NUM
	,TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.updated_at = Generate_Row_Num.UPDATED_AT
FROM
	$DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_FACT_OFFERING_INSTANCE TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID
JOIN
Generate_Row_Num Generate_Row_Num
ON
TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.partner_key = Generate_Row_Num.V_PARTNER_KEY AND TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.intervention_key = Generate_Row_Num.V_INTERVENTION_KEY AND TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.person_key = Generate_Row_Num.V_PERSON_KEY AND TGT_fact_offering_instance_UPD_$$RUNID.offering_key = Generate_Row_Num.V_OFFERING_KEY
 AND 
Generate_Row_Num.ROW_NUM =1

	PERSON_PID varchar(50)
	,INTERVENTION_PID varchar(50)
	,OFFERING_PID varchar(50)

rce_DxSubUnits.cmd:
SELECT 
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(TRIM(CAST(TRIM(CAST(SRC_vaccine_results_ods.PERSON_PID AS CHAR)) AS CHAR)),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS PERSON_PID,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(TRIM(CAST(TRIM(CAST(SRC_vaccine_results_ods.INTERVENTION_PID AS CHAR)) AS CHAR)),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS INTERVENTION_PID,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(TRIM(CAST(TRIM(CAST(SRC_vaccine_results_ods.OFFERING_PID AS CHAR)) AS CHAR)),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS OFFERING_PID,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(TRIM(CAST(TRIM(CAST(SRC_vaccine_results_ods.PARTNER_PID AS CHAR)) AS CHAR)),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS PARTNER_PID,
	coalesce(REPLACE(REPLACE(TRIM(CAST(TRIM(CAST(SRC_vaccine_results_ods.STATUS AS CHAR)) AS CHAR)),char(10),char(05)),char(13),char(06)),'NULL') AS STATUS,
	coalesce(DATE_FORMAT(TRIM(CAST(TRIM(CAST(SRC_vaccine_results_ods.ASSIGNED_AT AS CHAR)) AS CHAR)),'%Y-%m-%d'),'NULL') AS ASSIGNED_AT,
	coalesce(DATE_FORMAT(TRIM(CAST(TRIM(CAST(SRC_vaccine_results_ods.ORDER_DATE AS CHAR)) AS CHAR)),'%Y-%m-%d'),'NULL') AS ORDER_DATE,
	coalesce(DATE_FORMAT(DATE(SRC_vaccine_results_ods.date_of_service ),'%Y-%m-%d'),'NULL') AS SERVICE_DATE
 FROM ( 
SELECT SRC_person_offering_ods.person_pid AS person_pid 
      ,SRC_person_offering_ods.client_intervention_pid AS intervention_pid
      ,SRC_person_offering_ods.client_offering_pid AS offering_pid
      ,SRC_partner_offering_ods.partner_pid AS partner_pid
      ,SRC_person_intervention_ods.status
      ,MAX(SRC_person_intervention_ods.src_created_at) AS ASSIGNED_AT
      ,MAX(SRC_vaccine_results_ods.date_of_service) AS DATE_OF_SERVICE

 INNER JOIN bold_ods.person_vaccine_ods AS SRC_person_vaccine_ods 
    ON SRC_person_vaccine_ods.vaccine_result_pid = SRC_vaccine_results_ods.vaccine_results_pid 
   AND SRC_person_vaccine_ods.is_current = 1
 INNER JOIN bold_ods.person_offering_ods AS SRC_person_offering_ods 
    ON SRC_person_offering_ods.person_vaccine_pid = SRC_person_vaccine_ods.person_vaccine_pid 
   AND SRC_person_offering_ods.is_current = 1
 INNER JOIN bold_ods.person_intervention_ods AS SRC_person_intervention_ods 
    ON SRC_person_intervention_ods.person_intervention_pid = SRC_person_offering_ods.person_intervention_pid 
   AND SRC_person_intervention_ods.is_current = 1 
 INNER JOIN bold_ods.partner_offering_ods AS SRC_partner_offering_ods 
    ON SRC_partner_offering_ods.offering_pid = SRC_person_offering_ods.client_offering_pid 
   AND SRC_partner_offering_ods.is_current = 1
WHERE SRC_vaccine_results_ods.vaccine_results_pid IS NOT NULL 
  AND SRC_vaccine_results_ods.is_current = 1
GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 4, 5

MERGE $DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_FACT_OFFERING_INSTANCE TGT_fact_offering_instance 
 USING $TFORM_EXPR_NAME EXPR_NAME 
  ON TGT_fact_offering_instance.source_system = EXPR_NAME.V_SOURCE_SYSTEM AND 
TGT_fact_offering_instance.service_date = EXPR_NAME.V_DATE_OF_SERVICE AND 
TGT_fact_offering_instance.person_key = EXPR_NAME.V_PERSON_KEY AND 
TGT_fact_offering_instance.intervention_key = EXPR_NAME.V_INTERVENTION_KEY AND 
TGT_fact_offering_instance.offering_key = EXPR_NAME.V_OFFERING_KEY AND 
TGT_fact_offering_instance.partner_key = EXPR_NAME.V_PARTNER_KEY
 WHEN MATCHED THEN 
UPDATE SET
	status = EXPR_NAME.V_STATUS
	,order_date = EXPR_NAME.V_ORDER_DATE
	,assigned_date = EXPR_NAME.V_ASSIGNED_AT
	,updated_at = EXPR_NAME.UPDATED_AT
	,is_deleted = EXPR_NAME.is_deleted
 WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN 
INSERT
(partner_key,intervention_key,person_key,offering_key,status,order_date,service_date,assigned_date,created_at,updated_at,is_deleted,source_system)
VALUES (
EXPR_NAME.V_PARTNER_KEY,
EXPR_NAME.V_INTERVENTION_KEY,
EXPR_NAME.V_PERSON_KEY,
EXPR_NAME.V_OFFERING_KEY,
EXPR_NAME.V_STATUS,
EXPR_NAME.V_ORDER_DATE,
EXPR_NAME.V_DATE_OF_SERVICE,
EXPR_NAME.V_ASSIGNED_AT,
EXPR_NAME.CREATED_AT,
EXPR_NAME.UPDATED_AT,
EXPR_NAME.is_deleted,
EXPR_NAME.V_SOURCE_SYSTEM)#SEMICOLON_DELIM#

rce_DxSubUnits.cmd:
WITH SRC_dim_person  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_dim_person.person_key AS PERSON_KEY
	,SRC_dim_person.person_pid AS PERSON_PID
 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_PERSON SRC_dim_person  
 WHERE 
	SRC_dim_person.source_system = 'V4' 
) 
,SRC_dim_offering  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_dim_offering.offering_key AS OFFERING_KEY
	,SRC_dim_offering.offering_pid AS OFFERING_PID
 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_OFFERING SRC_dim_offering  
 WHERE 
	SRC_dim_offering.source_system  = 'V4' 
) 
,SRC_dim_partner  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_dim_partner.partner_key AS PARTNER_KEY
	,SRC_dim_partner.partner_pid AS PARTNER_PID
 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_PARTNER SRC_dim_partner  
 WHERE 
	SRC_dim_partner.source_system  = 'V4' 
) 
,SRC_dim_intervention  AS 
( 
SELECT 
	SRC_dim_intervention.intervention_key AS INTERVENTION_KEY
	,SRC_dim_intervention.intervention_pid AS INTERVENTION_PID
 FROM 
	$DO_GHL1_MS_IDM_DIM_INTERVENTION SRC_dim_intervention  
 WHERE 
	SRC_dim_intervention.source_system  = 'V4' 
) 
SELECT
VENN_GRP_NAME.V_STATUS AS V_STATUS,
VENN_GRP_NAME.V_ASSIGNED_AT AS V_ASSIGNED_AT,
VENN_GRP_NAME.V_ORDER_DATE AS V_ORDER_DATE,
VENN_GRP_NAME.V_SOURCE_SYSTEM AS V_SOURCE_SYSTEM,
VENN_GRP_NAME.V_DATE_OF_SERVICE AS V_DATE_OF_SERVICE,
SRC_dim_person.PERSON_KEY AS PERSON_KEY,
SRC_dim_person.PERSON_PID AS PERSON_PID,
SRC_dim_offering.OFFERING_KEY AS OFFERING_KEY,
SRC_dim_offering.OFFERING_PID AS OFFERING_PID,
SRC_dim_partner.PARTNER_KEY AS PARTNER_KEY,
SRC_dim_partner.PARTNER_PID AS PARTNER_PID,
SRC_dim_intervention.INTERVENTION_KEY AS INTERVENTION_KEY,
SRC_dim_intervention.INTERVENTION_PID AS INTERVENTION_PID
INTO $TFORM_JNR_NAME
 FROM $TFORM_VENN_GRP_NAME VENN_GRP_NAME 
INNER JOIN
SRC_dim_person 
ON
(VENN_GRP_NAME.V_PERIOD_PID = SRC_dim_person.PERSON_PID ) 
INNER JOIN
SRC_dim_offering 
ON
(VENN_GRP_NAME.V_OFFERING_PID = SRC_dim_offering.OFFERING_PID) 
INNER JOIN
SRC_dim_partner 
ON
(VENN_GRP_NAME.V_PARTNER_PID = SRC_dim_partner.PARTNER_PID ) 
INNER JOIN
SRC_dim_intervention 
ON
(VENN_GRP_NAME.V_INTERVENTION_PID = SRC_dim_intervention.INTERVENTION_PID )
